'''2015年南卡羅萊納州查爾斯頓槍擊案'''，是指發生於2015年6月17日，在[[美國|美國]][[南卡羅萊納州|南卡羅萊納州]][[查爾斯頓_(南卡羅來納州)|查爾斯頓]]的一起重大槍擊案。一名[[白人|白人]]在當地的一座[[非裔美國人|黑人]]教堂開槍，造成九人死亡，其中包括一名議員<ref name=appletw>{{cite news|author1=桂家齊 (翻譯)|title=【更新】美非裔教堂遭槍擊9死　警：應為仇殺事件|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/new/20150618/631282/|accessdate=2015-06-18|agency=[[台灣蘋果日報|台灣蘋果日報]]|date=2015-06-18}}</ref>。

案件發生於當地時間17日晚上，一座[[伊曼紐爾非裔衛理公會教堂|伊曼紐爾非裔衛理公會教堂]]（Emanuel African Methodist Episcopal Church）遭到一名年約20歲的白人男子亂槍掃射，多人當場死亡；嫌犯開槍後逃逸，警方对他进行全面[[通緝|通緝]]<ref name=itntw>{{cite news|title=美國非裔教堂槍擊案 9人慘死 嫌犯逃逸|url=http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1352588|accessdate=2015-06-18|agency=[[自由時報|自由時報]]|date=2015-06-18|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618155055/http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/world/breakingnews/1352588|dead-url=no}}</ref>。案發後14小時，他在[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]]被捕<ref name="HARRIET MCLEOD"/>。

2015年9月，南卡羅來納州的[[州檢察官|州檢察官]]求處兇嫌[[死刑|死刑]]<ref name=BBC20150903>{{cite news|title=Charleston shootings: Death penalty sought for Dylann Roof|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34146798|accessdate=2015-09-04|agency=BBC|date=2015-09-03|language=en|archive-date=2015-09-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905112109/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-34146798|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2016年12月，被告人迪倫·鲁夫被判33項罪名成立，2017年1月10日被判處死刑<ref>{{Cite news |url=http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-38578735 |title=美国南卡杀害9名黑人枪手鲁夫被判死刑 |work=BBC中文網 |date=2017-01-10 |accessdate=2017-01-11 |archive-date=2017-01-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170112202246/http://www.bbc.com/zhongwen/simp/world-38578735 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

== 背景 ==
{{main|美以美會}}
[[伊曼紐爾非裔衛理公會教堂|伊曼紐爾非裔衛理公會教堂]]，或譯'''伊曼紐爾非裔美以美會教堂'''，是一所在该州历史上发挥着重要角色的教堂，拥有199年的历史，见证了奴隶制时代、20世纪60年代民权运动和黑人生活问题运动<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/10/magazine/our-demand-is-simple-stop-killing-us.html|title='Our Demand Is Simple: Stop Killing Us'|work=[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]|date=2015-05-04|first=Jay Caspian|last=Kang|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618213838/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/05/10/magazine/our-demand-is-simple-stop-killing-us.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。教堂始建于1816年，是南方历史最悠久的非洲卫理公会教堂，被称为“伊曼纽尔之母”<ref name=CNN-Shooting-2015>{{cite news|last1=Payne|first1=Ed|title=Charleston church shooting: Multiple fatalities in South Carolina, source says|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/17/us/charleston-south-carolina-shooting/|accessdate=2015-06-18|work=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2015-06-18|archive-date=2019-01-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190104014643/https://www.cnn.com/2015/06/17/us/charleston-south-carolina-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name=Mullikin-CivilRightsRide-2013>{{cite web|last1=Pinckney|first1=Reverend Honorable Clementa C.|title=Civil Rights Ride 2013 – Clementa C. Pinckney, SC Senate, Pastor Mother Emanuel A.M.E.|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XP35_JVnP6g|website=Mullikin Law Firm|6=|accessdate=2015-06-18|date=2015-02-20|archive-date=2019-04-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190402173756/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=XP35_JVnP6g|dead-url=no}}</ref>。巴尔的摩黑人长期以来在此聚集。1822年教堂的联合创建人丹麦克·维西（Denmark Vesey）企图发动奴隶叛乱，导致自己被处决，教堂亦被烧毁<ref name=PostCourier-NineShot-2015>{{cite news|url=http://www.postandcourier.com/article/20150617/PC16/150619408|title=Nine shot, multiple fatalities reported in downtown church shooting|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2016-07-28|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160728072115/http://www.postandcourier.com/article/20150617/PC16/150619408|dead-url=no}}</ref>直至1834年得以重建<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.euronews.com/2015/06/18/us-at-least-9-dead-in-hate-crime-shooting-in-charleston/|title=US: at least 9 killed in Charleston church massacre|work=Euronews|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618133054/http://www.euronews.com/2015/06/18/us-at-least-9-dead-in-hate-crime-shooting-in-charleston/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

案发当时，皮克林正举行集会悼念4月4日在北查尔斯顿被白人警察杀害的沃尔特·斯科特（{{lang|en|Walter Scott}}）。皮克林是州参议员，倡导以法律规定警察必须随身佩戴摄像机<ref name="Heavy-Pinckney5Fact-2015">{{cite news|last1 = Cleary|first1 = Tom|title = Clementa Pinckney Dead: 5 Fast Facts You Need to Know|url = http://heavy.com/news/2015/06/clementa-pinckney-dead-charleston-church-shooting-victim-black-church-pastor-ame-shot-injury/|accessdate = 2015-06-17|work = Heavy.com|date = 2015-06-18|archive-date = 2017-12-24|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20171224100139/http://heavy.com/news/2015/06/clementa-pinckney-dead-charleston-church-shooting-victim-black-church-pastor-ame-shot-injury/|dead-url = no}}</ref>。密歇根州州立大学政治学家罗伯特·米奇指出，伊曼纽尔袭击案和1963年[[阿拉巴马州|阿拉巴马州]][[伯明翰_(阿拉巴马州)|伯明翰]]政治上活跃的非裔教会的袭击案有一些相似之处，在那次事件中，[[三K党|三K党]]杀害了四名黑人女孩，另有14人受伤，时值20世纪60年代正在势头上的民权运动<ref name=":0">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/18/for-charlestons-emanuel-a-m-e-church-one-of-the-oldest-in-america-shooting-is-another-painful-chapter-in-long-history/|title=For Charleston's Emanuel AME Church, shooting is another painful chapter in rich history|first=Sarah|last=Kaplan|work=The Washington Post|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618111958/http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/18/for-charlestons-emanuel-a-m-e-church-one-of-the-oldest-in-america-shooting-is-another-painful-chapter-in-long-history/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。许多学者、新闻记者、活动家和政治家都强调需要了解全国范围内更为广泛的种族主义袭击，而不是将其看作出于种族动机的孤立暴力事件<ref>{{Cite web|title = Thugs and Terrorists Have Attacked Black Churches for Generations|url = http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2015/06/thugs-and-terrorists-have-plagued-black-churches-for-generations/396212/|date = 2015-06-18|accessdate = 2015-06-18|work = The Atlantic|first = Connor|last = Friedersdorf|archive-date = 2015-06-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618115824/http://www.theatlantic.com/politics/archive/2015/06/thugs-and-terrorists-have-plagued-black-churches-for-generations/396212/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite news|script-title = en:Shooters of color are called ‘terrorists’ and ‘thugs.’ Why are white shooters called ‘mentally ill’?|url = http://www.washingtonpost.com/posteverything/wp/2015/06/18/call-the-charleston-church-shooting-what-it-is-terrorism/|newspaper = [[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|date = 2015-06-18|access-date = 2015-06-18|issn = 0190-8286|language = en-US|first = Anthea|last = Butler|archive-date = 2015-06-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618200132/http://www.washingtonpost.com/posteverything/wp/2015/06/18/call-the-charleston-church-shooting-what-it-is-terrorism/|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Black lives - and churches - matter|url = http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/opinion/2015/06/black-lives-churches-matter-charleston-150618060102973.html|website = www.aljazeera.com|date = 2015-06-18|access-date = 2015-06-18|6 = |archive-date = 2015-06-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618193808/http://www.aljazeera.com/indepth/opinion/2015/06/black-lives-churches-matter-charleston-150618060102973.html|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title = Terrorism in Charleston demands the government act like black lives matter {{!}} The Rev Broderick Greer|url = http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2015/jun/18/terrorism-charleston-government-black-lives-matter|website = [[卫报|卫报]]|date = 2015-06-18|access-date = 2015-06-18|first = Reverend Broderick|last = Greer|archive-date = 2015-06-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618212420/http://www.theguardian.com/commentisfree/2015/jun/18/terrorism-charleston-government-black-lives-matter|dead-url = no}}</ref>。

== 經過 ==
[[File:Charleston_Shooting_Memorial_Service.jpg|缩略图]]
根據查爾斯頓市警察局的說法，一名身穿灰色運動衫，藍色[[牛仔褲|牛仔褲]]的白人男子，於當地時間17日晚上九時許，在教堂之中進行掃射，當時教堂內正在舉行聖經研究會<ref name=chinanews>{{cite news|title=美國南卡羅萊納州發生槍擊案 或致多人傷亡|url=http://big5.chinanews.com/gj/2015/06-18/7352740.shtml|accessdate=2015-06-18|agency=[[中新網|中新網]]|date=2015-06-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618174406/http://big5.chinanews.com/gj/2015/06-18/7352740.shtml|archivedate=2015-06-18}}</ref>；而死者之一已被證實是州參議員[[克萊門塔·平克尼|克萊門塔·平克尼]]（{{lang|en|Clementa C. Pinckney}}），他身兼教會[[牧師|牧師]]<ref name=rtitw>{{cite news|title=美南卡教會槍擊案 非裔州參議員遇害|url=http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=198287|accessdate=2015-06-18|agency=[[中央廣播電台|中央廣播電台]]|date=2015-06-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618172518/http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=198287|archivedate=2015-06-18|df=}}</ref>。

當時包括嫌犯在內，共有13人參加了聖經研究會<ref name="Bruce Wright">{{cite news|author1=Bruce Wright|script-title=en:Charleston Shooting Victims’ Names Revealed In South Carolina Church Massacre|url=http://www.ibtimes.com/charleston-shooting-victims-names-revealed-south-carolina-church-massacre-1973630|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=ibtimes|date=2015-06-18|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619175344/http://www.ibtimes.com/charleston-shooting-victims-names-revealed-south-carolina-church-massacre-1973630|dead-url=no}}</ref>。根據倖存者的說法，嫌犯在研究會中，坐在平克尼附近聆聽他的講道約1小時。接著，當他們討論聖經的過程中，他不同意大家的說法；過了一會，他突然掏出槍，瞄準了87歲的苏珊·杰克逊（{{lang|en|Susie Jackson}}）女士<ref name=CNN>{{cite news|title=Family remembers matriarch killed in Charleston shooting|url=http://edition.cnn.com/videos/tv/2015/06/19/susie-jackson-remembered-tuchman-sot-ac.cnn|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[CNN|CNN]]|date=2015-06-19|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619152857/http://edition.cnn.com/videos/tv/2015/06/19/susie-jackson-remembered-tuchman-sot-ac.cnn|dead-url=no}}</ref>；苏珊的[[外甥|外甥]]，26歲的迪万扎·桑德斯（{{lang|en|Tywanza Sanders}}）試圖阻止他，並問他為什麼要攻擊教友<ref name=wsj.com>{{cite news|author1=NATHAN KOPPEL and  ANA CAMPOY|title=Charleston Shooting Victims Were Drawn Together by Their Faith|url=http://www.wsj.com/articles/tywanza-sanders-church-shooting-victim-called-quiet-industrious-1434660835|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[華爾街日報|華爾街日報]]|date=2015-06-18|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619014952/http://www.wsj.com/articles/tywanza-sanders-church-shooting-victim-called-quiet-industrious-1434660835|dead-url=no}}</ref>，嫌犯回答稱：「你們（黑人）[[強姦|強姦]]我們的婦女，侵占我們的國家，你們必須消失。」，並稱他打算殺光所有黑人，說完隨即開槍<ref name=storm.mg />。於是擋在苏珊身前的迪万扎，成為第一位遇害者<ref name=wsj.com />。

過程中，嫌犯一邊辱罵[[種族歧視|種族歧視]]的言語與[[粗話|粗話]]，一邊開槍殺人，期間還裝填了五次彈藥<ref name=dailymail.co.uk>{{cite news|author1=Lydia Warren and Laura Collins and Josh Gardner|title=Charleston shooting suspect Dylann Roof was given a gun for his birthday|url=http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3129887/Dylann-Roof-21-suspected-murdering-nine-race-hate-church-crime-got-gun-birthday-arrested-twice-year-drug-trespassing-charges.html|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[每日郵報|每日郵報]]|date=2015-06-18|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619013011/http://www.dailymail.co.uk/news/article-3129887/Dylann-Roof-21-suspected-murdering-nine-race-hate-church-crime-got-gun-birthday-arrested-twice-year-drug-trespassing-charges.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。桑德斯的母親，也是研究會參加者之一稱，其他倖存者是透過[[假死|裝死]]才躲過了槍擊；而她是嫌犯刻意留下的活口，嫌犯對她說，「這樣她就可以告訴大家發生了什麼事」<ref name=independent.co.uk>{{cite news|author1=ADAM WITHNALL|title=Charleston shooting: Five-year-old child who 'played dead' among survivors in South Carolina|url=http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/charleston-shooting-fiveyearold-child-who-played-dead-among-survivors-in-south-carolina-10327938.html|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[獨立報|獨立報]]|date=2015-06-18|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618212555/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/charleston-shooting-fiveyearold-child-who-played-dead-among-survivors-in-south-carolina-10327938.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。9名死者都是黑人，8人是當場死亡，另一人是在[[醫院|醫院]][[急救|急救]]無效宣告不治<ref name=BBC>{{cite news|title=Charleston church shooting: Nine die in South Carolina 'hate crime'|url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33179019|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[BBC|BBC]]|date=2015-06-18|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618233353/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-us-canada-33179019|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

18日，[[美國聯邦調查局|美國聯邦調查局]]（FBI）已鎖定了一名21歲金髮白人男子迪倫·鲁夫（Dylann Roof）為兇手<ref name=rtitw2>{{cite news|author1=張子清 (翻譯)|title=美非裔教會槍手 已確認身份|url=http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=198402|accessdate=2015-06-18|agency=中央廣播電台|date=2015-06-18|deadurl=yes|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618201446/http://news.rti.org.tw/news/detail/?recordId=198402|archivedate=2015-06-18|df=}}</ref>；案發後的14小時，警方宣布在[[北卡羅萊納州|北卡羅萊納州]]的一處{{link-en|臨檢|Traffic stop}}點抓到了他，距離案發地點220[[公里|公里]]<ref name="HARRIET MCLEOD">{{cite news|author1=HARRIET MCLEOD|title=White suspect arrested in killing of nine at black U.S. church|url=http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/18/us-usa-shooting-south-carolina-idUSKBN0OY06A20150618|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[路透社|路透社]]|date=2015-06-18|language=en|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619010505/http://www.reuters.com/article/2015/06/18/us-usa-shooting-south-carolina-idUSKBN0OY06A20150618|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

