'''迪倫·斯托姆·魯夫'''（{{lang-en|Dylann Storm Roof}}），1994年4月3日生於[[南卡羅來納州|南卡羅來納州]][[哥伦比亚_(南卡罗来纳州)|哥倫比亞市]]。警方調查時，發現在他的[[臉書|臉書]]大頭照中，他穿著一件印有兩面國旗的夾克，一是1994年以前的[[南非國旗|南非國旗]]，一是[[羅德西亞|羅德西亞]]（後稱[[辛巴威|辛巴威]]）的國旗，兩個國家在當時都曾嚴格施行[[種族隔離|種族隔離]]制度<ref name=storm.mg>{{cite news|author1=閻紀宇|title=「我要殺黑人」美國教堂血案殺手行兇前告白|url=http://www.storm.mg/article/53974|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=[[風傳媒|風傳媒]]|date=2015-06-19|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619195023/http://www.storm.mg/article/53974|dead-url=no}}</ref>；案發前，他曾跟朋友預告將要殺人，但朋友都以為他是在開玩笑，沒有多加留意<ref name=appletw2>{{cite news|author1=余浚安|title=教堂濫殺白人憤青　上周曾跟朋友預告計畫|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150619/632256/%E6%95%99%E5%A0%82%E6%BF%AB%E6%AE%BA%E7%99%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%86%A4%E9%9D%92%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E6%9B%BE%E8%B7%9F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=台灣蘋果日報|date=2015-06-19|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621181803/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150619/632256/%E6%95%99%E5%A0%82%E6%BF%AB%E6%AE%BA%E7%99%BD%E4%BA%BA%E6%86%A4%E9%9D%92%E3%80%80%E4%B8%8A%E5%91%A8%E6%9B%BE%E8%B7%9F%E6%9C%8B%E5%8F%8B%E9%A0%90%E5%91%8A%E8%A8%88%E7%95%AB/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

案發後，他的叔叔卡森·考尔斯（{{lang|en|Carson Cowles}}）從[[電視新聞|電視新聞]]畫面中確認是自己的[[姪子|姪子]]，並稱迪倫在4月份生日時，曾收到父親所送的生日禮物：一把點45[[手槍|手槍]]，但他無法確認該把手槍是否為本次犯案的凶器<ref name=appletw3>{{cite news|author1=余浚安|title=害羞青年變憤青　21歲生日爸爸送他手槍|url=http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150618/631796/%E5%AE%B3%E7%BE%9E%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%AE%8A%E6%86%A4%E9%9D%92%E3%80%8021%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E9%80%81%E4%BB%96%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D|accessdate=2015-06-19|agency=台灣蘋果日報|date=2015-06-18|archive-date=2015-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150621003758/http://www.appledaily.com.tw/realtimenews/article/international/20150618/631796/%E5%AE%B3%E7%BE%9E%E9%9D%92%E5%B9%B4%E8%AE%8A%E6%86%A4%E9%9D%92%E3%80%8021%E6%AD%B2%E7%94%9F%E6%97%A5%E7%88%B8%E7%88%B8%E9%80%81%E4%BB%96%E6%89%8B%E6%A7%8D|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==受害者==
所有受害者均为黑人，其中有六人为女性，三人为男性。有八人当场死亡，第九位死者丹尼尔·西蒙斯（{{lang|en|Daniel Simmons}}）送院后死亡<ref name="EverythingKnown">{{cite web|url=http://time.com/3926112/charleston-shooting-latest/|title=Everything We Know About the Charleston Shooting|work=[[时代_(杂志)|TIME]]|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618115853/http://time.com/3926112/charleston-shooting-latest/|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="ShootingSuspect">{{cite web|url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/18/us/charleston-church-shooting-suspect/|title=Who is the Charleston church shooting suspect?|work=[[CNN|CNN.com]]|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2015-06-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150618212548/http://www.cnn.com/2015/06/18/us/charleston-church-shooting-suspect/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。所有人的死因均为近距离枪杀<ref name="SuspectCaptured">{{cite web|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/17/white-gunman-sought-in-shooting-at-historic-charleston-african-ame-church/|title=Church shooting suspect Dylann Roof captured amid hate crime investigation|work=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2019-05-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190509205857/https://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/17/white-gunman-sought-in-shooting-at-historic-charleston-african-ame-church/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。另一人负伤后幸存。受害者的身份为<ref>{{Cite web|title = Charleston Shooting Victims Identified|url = http://abcnews.go.com/US/charleston-shooting-victims-identified/story?id=31863489|website = [[ABC|ABC News]]|date = 2015-06-18|accessdate = 2015-06-18|archive-date = 2015-06-18|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150618212547/http://abcnews.go.com/US/charleston-shooting-victims-identified/story?id=31863489|dead-url = no}}</ref>：
