0150619175407/http://www.independent.co.uk/news/world/americas/charleston-shooting-live-suspect-dylann-roof-in-custody-as-us-mourns-church-massacre--live-updates-10330694.html|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="RoofConfessed">{{cite web|url=http://abcnews.go.com/US/dylann-roof-confessed-killing-people-charleston-church-source/story?id=31884893|title=Dylann Roof Confessed to Killing 9 People at AME Church, Source Says|work=[[ABC|ABC News]]|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-06-19|6=|first=Josh|last=Margolin|first2=Emily|last2=Shapiro|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619151302/http://abcnews.go.com/US/dylann-roof-confessed-killing-people-charleston-church-source/story?id=31884893|dead-url=no}}</ref>，当天晚些时候在法庭的保释听证中首次受审<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/charleston-church-shooting/dylann-roof-almost-didnt-go-through-charleston-church-shooting-n378341|title=Dylann Roof 'Almost Didn't Go Through' With Charleston Church Shooting|work=[[NBC|NBC News]]|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-06-19|first=Daniel|last=Arkin|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619132528/http://www.nbcnews.com/storyline/charleston-church-shooting/dylann-roof-almost-didnt-go-through-charleston-church-shooting-n378341|dead-url=no}}</ref>。州长尼克·黑利呼吁检察官判处魯夫[[死刑|死刑]]<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.bostonglobe.com/news/nation/2015/06/19/the-latest-church-shooting-haley-calls-for-death-penalty/Sd50001xUfcaWDV1XdZxHM/story.html|title=S.C. governor calls for death penalty in church shooting|work=[[波士顿环球报|波士顿环球报]]|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-06-19|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619175307/https://www.bostonglobe.com/news/nation/2015/06/19/the-latest-church-shooting-haley-calls-for-death-penalty/Sd50001xUfcaWDV1XdZxHM/story.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

在查尔斯顿的莫里斯·布朗非洲卫理公会教堂，不同种族和宗教的人士参加悼念受害者的纪念仪式，宣称这种袭击不会分裂社会<ref name="BroughtBack"/>。

阿拉巴馬州蒙哥马利[[南方贫困法律中心|南方贫困法律中心]]情报项目主任海蒂·贝利奇，長期追踪美国的仇恨团体，她表示枪手报告的评论反映出白人至上主义网络论坛的主流意见。目前正在调查犯罪嫌疑人是否与任何的仇恨团体有联系，贝利奇表示，这些团体的数量过去十年来一直在增长，“南卡罗来纳州有好几年是仇恨团体最集中的地方<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Justice/2015/0618/Charleston-mass-shooting-Reminder-of-past-racist-attacks-on-black-churches|title=Charleston mass shooting: Reminder of past racist attacks on black churches|work=The Christian Science Monitor|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2017-10-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171005144243/https://www.csmonitor.com/USA/Justice/2015/0618/Charleston-mass-shooting-Reminder-of-past-racist-attacks-on-black-churches|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

美国总统[[奥巴马|奥巴马]]回应事件时聚集于枪支管控问题，他表示：“这种大规模的暴力事件不会在其他发达国家出现<ref>{{cite web|url=http://m.huffpost.com/us/entry/7613074|title=Obama On Charleston Shooting: 'This Type Of Mass Violence Does Not Happen In Other Advanced Countries'|work=The Huffington Post|date=2015-06-18|accessdate=2015-06-18|archive-date=2019-09-12|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190912055011/https://www.huffpost.com/entry/barack-obama-charleston-shooting_n_7613074|dead-url=no}}</ref>。”

案发翌日，南卡罗来纳州议会大厦[[下半旗|下半旗]]。然而，议会大厦附近的邦联士兵纪念碑照常升[[美利坚联盟国国旗|聯盟旗]]<ref>{{cite news|last1=Moyer|first1=Justin Wm.|title=Why South Carolina's Confederate flag isn't at half-staff after church shooting|url=http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/19/why-south-carolinas-confederate-flag-isnt-at-half-mast-after-church-shooting/|accessdate=2015-06-19|work=[[华盛顿邮报|华盛顿邮报]]|date=2015-06-19|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619121113/http://www.washingtonpost.com/news/morning-mix/wp/2015/06/19/why-south-carolinas-confederate-flag-isnt-at-half-mast-after-church-shooting/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。由于攻击事件，州议会再次呼吁撤掉被认为代表着种族隔离制度和蓄奴制度的聯盟旗<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/06/19/dylann-roof-charleston-police-charged-with-murder-black-church/28975573/|title=Dylann Roof charged with 9 counts of murder in Charleston attack|work=[[USA_Today|USA Today]]|date=2015-06-19|accessdate=2015-06-19|first=Yamiche|last=Alcindor|first2=Doug|last2=Stanglin|archive-date=2015-06-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150619152500/http://www.usatoday.com/story/news/nation/2015/06/19/dylann-roof-charleston-police-charged-with-murder-black-church/28975573/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

